Move

 

A system object can be part of another system object (Cultural Object, Project, Folder, etc.). To change the system object to which the current one is part of use Move action.

Cultural objects can't be moved

In the dialog:

  1. Enter search criteria to find the system object (cultural object, project, folder, etc.) to which the current object will be part of.
  2. Select the system object from the search result
  3. Press the Ok button
